(76, 0, 3, ',', 4, 5, '【微分享】教你快速找到最优图片', '<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span><img src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/gCCoZxeBZ1KM6C4UVM91K8CMbbMMKZ.jpg" height="284" width="553" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">你正在制作<span>PPT</span>课件，或是写一份报告，需要配一张图来说明，但是找来找去没有高清的图片，你急的焦头烂额，有好办法吗？</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">现在很多的搜索引擎都具备“以图找图，”的功能，它通过以图搜图的方式，帮你找到相似的图片。下面就介绍几个搜索引擎：</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D;">1</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D;">、<span>http://shitu.baidu.com </span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">百度“识图”（<span>shitu.baidu.com</span>）。让用户通过上传本地图片或者输入图片的<span>URL</span>地址之后，进而从互联网中搜索出与此相似的图片资源及信息内容。但需要注意的是，用户上传本地图片时，图片的文件要小于<span>5M</span>，格式可为<span>JPG</span>、<span>JPEG</span>、<span>GIF</span>、<span>PNG</span>、<span>BMP</span>等图片文件。</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"><img src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/mpixypfqyxYE7pPpDf7FxBDp9xyDsI.jpg" alt="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/9KywrkWzicWcDIiaMb8m8ibUQI9m7HZfmdnn8FVvFhbesrYCdicvMtXKbQ/0" height="125" width="580" /></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D;">2</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D;">、<span>http://images.google.com.hk</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">google</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">以图搜图，图片上传的方法有<span>3</span>种，你可以按下相机小图标（如下图），点击“上传图片”，然后选择本地图片进行上传；如果你使用<span> Chrome</span>、<span>FireFox </span>等先进的浏览器，还能直接把电脑上的图片拖放到输入框中进行搜索，这个相当的方便！！另外，如果你在网络上看到感兴趣的照片了，右键复制图片的网址，然后点击相机图标，然后在“粘贴图片地址”的地方输入也可以进行搜索。</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;" align="center">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"><img src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/IyR6oboY476aYjl2sZooAAmO77a7zB.jpg" alt="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/9KywrkWzicWcDIiaMb8m8ibUQI9m7HZfmdnvCic0ZpWiafUErjkgnc48OFQ/0" height="104" width="521" /></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">如果你的英文还不错的话，下面几个链接供你参考：</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">3</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">、<span>http://tineye.com/ </span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">TinEye</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">是加拿大<span>Id</span>é<span>e</span>公司研发的相似图片搜索引擎，<span>TinEye</span>主要用途有：<span>1</span>、发现图片的来源与相关信息；<span>2</span>、研究追踪图片信息在互联网的传播；<span>3</span>、找到高分辨率版本的图片；<span>4</span>、找到有你照片的网页；<span>5</span>、看看这张图片有哪些不同版本。</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"><img src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/rk0DF4z04sc50405dX5773z0xC73D3.jpg" alt="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/9KywrkWzicWcDIiaMb8m8ibUQI9m7HZfmdnlYvSALmKiclctgnyveUGIBQ/0" height="103" width="615" /></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">4</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">、<span>http://www.incogna.com</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">Incogna</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">的搜索速度非常快，主要是基于色彩和形状上的相似性。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<img src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/iePSEcNzf3hpz7HPqe7C17i3U755f8.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">5</span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#366092;">、<span>http://www.terragalleria.com</span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">Terragalleria</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;">主要基于视觉上的相似性，而不考虑图片的内容。</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"><img title="" src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/AZ5W6cnNtTa4xIK3Y3XPa5zTv94sP5.jpg" alt="" align="" height="" width="" /></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;"> </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;text-indent:6.0pt;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#82823F;">—— </span></b><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#82823F;">转自职场智慧</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">学习分享 无处不在</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">迈瑞管理学院，与您一同分享精彩文章</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">-------------------------------------</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;text-indent:6.0pt;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">欢迎关注迈瑞管理学院微信分享平台</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">（微信号：</span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">Management_Institute</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;">）</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;" align="left">\r\n	<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"><img title="" src="/las/resource/attachment/images/3/2014/03/f2WZU9Jw2922uDNR20MRUO9uMR1OIu.jpg" alt="" align="" height="" width="" /></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<span> </span> \r\n</p>', 'images/2014/03/jsws0oz9kffOKxXMrBS6GtbGoem9ok.jpg', '你正在制作PPT课件，或是写一份报告，需要配一张图...', '', 1394176564, 0),
